  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Monster Fighter, a 2D fighting game for everyone.<br><br>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/a1ffe4f532907f2fa68bc86f02470893.avif?t=1653649993\" width=600 height=320 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/TheGame.jpg?t=1653649993\" /></span><br><br>Face adorable Kaijus in fun battles to prove you are the strongest. <br>A game where you will test your skill by repeatedly pressing a single button. <br>Can you be the one finger fighting king?<br><br><strong>ATTENTION. This game is only for 2 players exclusively</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/History.jpg?t=1653649993\" /></span><br>Believe it or not, monsters exist and live in their own world.<br>One day one of them, the adorable Teddy Butcher Bear, decides to organize a fighting tournament by summoning them all to show their skills and find out who is the strongest...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/2771ceb7019c4c17ce27a83575118e98.avif?t=1653649993\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/239c992b470974dbdb6c499b893d5e74.webp?t=1653649993\" width=600 height=58 /></span><br><br>- Versus mode fighting game (1 vs 1).<br>- 12 wonderful monsters<br>- 12 fabulous scenarios<br>- 2 players (Cooperative mode only)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/20bdd1da61417a044b36b3669cf98a64.avif?t=1653649993\" width=600 height=336 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2>.<br>- Player 1 presses the A button.<br>- Player 2 presses the L button.<br>- Selection of characters and scenarios with the mouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790710/extras/df8eb3b1f454f032c3f037091dc3966a.avif?t=1653649993\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
